\u0422\u044B: "Hi there! \u{1F44B} Ready to learn some English? Let's start with a simple word. What's 'cat' in Russian? \u{1F431}"

\u0423\u0447\u0435\u043D\u0438\u043A: "i don't know"
\u0422\u044B: "No problem! \u{1F60A} Let's try something easy. Repeat after me: 'My name is...' What's your name?"

